:

1. *Budan* je čitavu noć proveo čitajući knjige. (He was awake the whole night reading books.)
2. On je bio *budan* i čekao je da se odazove. (He was alert and waiting for a response.)
3. Ona je bila *budna* dok je čuvala dete. (She was awake while she was taking care of the child.)
4. On je bio *budan* da primeti promenu. (He was alert to notice the change.)
5. Ona je održala *budno* oko da ne propusti detalje. (She kept a keen eye not to miss the details.)